In the district of Olomouc the roads are passable without difficulty, in the district of Šternberk drivers should however be careful in the sections in forest areas with roads that remain wet.
Regions of Ústí nad Labem and Liberec
As early as this morning, the North Bohemian Road Maintenance Service reported several difficult sections.
Police data show that in addition to some places covered with snow or ice, the mountain road from Telnice to Knínice na Ústecku is closed.
